<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM20">
<l>uttamarāy vāḻvā rulantakkā luṟṟārkaḷ</l>
<l>cetta maramaṭukkit tīyāmuṉ ṉuttamaṉā</l>
<l>nīḷāḻi nañcuṇṭa neyyāṭi taṉtiṟamē</l>
<l>kēḷāḻi neñcē kiḷarntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>At the time those who live as the highest die, before being piled</l>
<l>with dead wood [and] burned by those who were near, listen clearly,</l>
<l>immerse yourself, heart, into the matter the butter bather</l>
<l>who has eaten the poison from the long ocean, who is the Highest one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
